  "text": "3. As there are no previous methods for direct comparison, we propose several baselines and compare performance against all of those. [CITATION_1] . We show experimental results on standard few-shot testing benchmarks such as mini-ImageNet [CITATION_2] and tiered-ImageNet [CITATION_3] .",
